{"title":"深井的岗位","authors":["卞国福"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":12,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"深井的岗位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卞国福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在深井里只有钻声和水声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水滴答着只有泥沙和碎石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从嶙峋的井壁跌落下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一双把着风钻的大手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目光吞食着坚硬的地壳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有白天没有黑夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有在矿床上独立的意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掘进着沉默的时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是与黑暗的一场剧烈的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"较量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是与光明的一次庄严的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}